	* appl/bsd/rsh.c (main): make sure not to send `-K' before the
 	hostname when re-execing

	* appl/bsd/su.c: openlog LOG_AUTH

Fri Jul 24 1998

	* lib/krb/create_ciph.c: typo: s/tmp/rem/

