Sun Nov 9 1997

	* Release 0.9.7


	* configure.in: test for ssize_t

	* appl/bsd/rlogind.c: Fill in ut_type, and ut_exit if they exist.

	* appl/kx/common.c (create_and_write_cookie): Create temp file
 	with mkstemp.


