	* lib/krb/krb_get_in_tkt.c: New function tf_setup.

Sat Feb 15 1997

	* man/otp.1: updated

	* appl/otp/otp.c: New options `-d' and `-r'.  From Fabien COELHO
 	<coelho@cri.ensmp.fr>

