 	of UIDL-string.

Sun Nov 24 1996

	* Release 0.9.3

Sat Nov 23 1996

	* kadmin/ksrvutil_get.c: Use `krb_unparse_name_long' Better
 	defaults.

	* lib/krb/krb.h: Added *_to_key

	* lib/krb/get_svc_in_tkt.c (srvtab_to_key): Make public

